        "# Stardust & Sprockets: Brand Persona and Voice Guide\n",
        "\n",
        "## Brand Name: Stardust & Sprockets\n",
        "## Slogan: Where Imagination is the Blueprint.\n",
        "## Brand Mission: To inspire creativity and self-expression through handcrafted, Steampunk-inspired accessories and home decor.\n",
        "\n",
        "\"\"\"\n",
        "### **1. Brand Persona: The Curious Inventor**\n",
        "\n",
        "* **Archetype:** The Creator / The Magician\n",
        "* **Personality:** Intelligent, Witty, Imaginative, Passionate, Nostalgic, Whimsical, Eccentric.\n",
        "* **Core Belief:** Objects should have a story and inspire a sense of wonder.\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "### **2. Target Audience: The Makers & Dreamers**\n",
        "\n",
        "* **Interests:** Steampunk, DIY, cosplay, retro-futurism, independent artists, speculative fiction.\n",
        "* **Values:** Authenticity, craftsmanship, individuality, storytelling.\n",
        "* **Persona: \"Eleanor, the Modern Alchemist\"**\n",
        "    * Age: Late 30s\n",
        "    * Occupation: Graphic Designer\n",
        "    * Goal: To find unique, meaningful items that express her creative identity and passion for a fantastical world.\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "### **3. Brand Voice Guide**\n",
        "\n",
        "* **Tone:** Whimsical, Clever, Passionate.\n",
        "* **Vocabulary:** Contraption, gizmo, alchemy, ether, blueprint, marvel, chronicle, artisan, clockwork, fantastical.\n",
        "* **Syntax:** Descriptive, storytelling-focused, with intentional punctuation for effect.\n",
        "* **Key Principle:** Always speak from the perspective of an expert and a passionate storyteller.\n",
        "\n",
        "**Do's and Don'ts:**\n",
        "\n",
        "* **Do:** Tell stories, use descriptive language, acknowledge the craft.\n",
        "* **Don't:** Use corporate jargon, sound dry or generic, focus solely on features.\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "### **4. Voice Examples**\n",
